  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Effect of PF-03463275 on Specific Cognitive Domains</measure>
    <time_frame>Change from baseline in cognitive measures at approximately 5 weeks</time_frame>
    <description>To test the efficacy of PF-03463275 on cognitive test performance specifically, with change in specific cognitive domains including verbal and visual learning and short-term/working memory examined as exploratory analyses.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
